data.description: Price Change, -  Nice 3+2, 1294 sq. ft., front to back entrance, chain  link fence, 2 car garage with garage door opener, This house come with stove, refrigerator, garbage disposal, washer and dryer hook-up, central  air and heating conditioning, water softener and sprinklers (Buyer to Verify), carpet, tile floor, nice fireplace with brownish stone-like background in living-room. Cover patio and two tool sheds.The house is being clean-up and sellers will negotiation, the yard will cleaned especially. The house is in good condition but buyers should always verify all conditions.
